s%20I%20had%20been%20using.%20The%20gentle%20curved%20shape%20was%20everything%20I%20needed.%20My%20head%20felt%20supported%2C%20my%20shoulder%20had%20plenty%20of%20space%2C%20and%20I%20wasn't%20constantly%20shifting%20around%20to%20get%20comfortable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20soft%2C%20a%20little%20plush%2C%20and%20has%20just%20enough%20give%20that%20you%20won't%20have%20to%20fight%20it%20into%20place.%20That%20part%20clicked%20in%20right%20away%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20weeks%20in%2C%20though%2C%20I%20started%20to%20notice%20that%20my%20head%20was%20sinking%20a%20little%20more%20than%20I%20wanted.%20It%20wasn't%20uncomfortable%2C%20but%20I%20did%20wake%20up%20a%20few%20times%20to%20adjust%20it%20throughout%20the%20night.%20It's%20filled%20with%20a%20mix%20of%20cross-cut%20memory%20foam%20and%20microfiber%2C%20giving%20it%20a%20soft%2C%20plush%20feel.%20But%20that%20also%20means%20it%20can%20compress%20a%20little%20if%20you%20don't%20have%20the%20right%20loft%20dialed%20in.%20Adding%20some%20of%20the%20extra%20fill%20to%20the%20center%20of%20the%20pillow%20and%20gently%20molding%20it%20into%20place%20was%20the%20fix.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20liner%20and%20fill%20in%20the%20Coop%20Original%20Crescent%20pillow%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f8cb3e3022d9b19bc002da%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20liner%20and%20fill%20in%20the%20Coop%20Original%20Crescent%20pillow%3Cp%3EBronwyn%20Barnes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20adjustability%20is%20the%20real%20value%20of%20the%20Coop%20pillow.%20You're%20not%20stuck%20with%20whatever%20loft%20it%20comes%20with.%20You%20can%20make%20it%20perfect%20for%20your%20particular%20sleep%20needs.%20Because%20it%20leans%20softer%2C%20I%20sometimes%20used%20an%20extra%20pillow%20to%20give%20me%20a%20little%20extra%20height%20when%20I%20was%20sitting%20up%20in%20bed%20to%20read