%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecooling%20pillowcase%3C%2Fa%3E%20that's%20made%20from%20cooling%20nylon%20spandex.%20The%20pillow%20shape%20will%20also%20work%20with%20most%20envelope-style%20pillowcases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Coop%20is%20softer%20and%20more%20forgiving.%20If%20you%20like%20a%20plush%20pillow%20or%20aren't%20sure%20what%20loft%20is%20right%20for%20you%2C%20it's%20the%20best%20place%20to%20start.%20You%20can%20tweak%20the%20fill%20level%20until%20it%20feels%20just%20right%2C%20and%20once%20you%20do%2C%20the%20difference%20is%20noticeable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Eli%20%26amp%3B%20Elm%20is%20more%20structured.%20The%20shape%20is%20more%20defined%2C%20the%20support%20is%20more%20consistent%2C%20and%20it%20feels%20dialed%20in%20right%20out%20of%20the%20box.%20I%20moved%20around%20much%20less%20when%20I%20slept%20on%20it%2C%20and%20didn't%20feel%20the%20need%20to%20adjust%20the%20fill%20level%20or%20the%20shape%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20ultimately%20why%20the%20Eli%20%26amp%3B%20Elm%20edged%20out%20the%20Coop%20Original%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEither%20way%2C%20the%20biggest%20upgrade%20is%20the%20shape.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Eli%20%26amp%3B%20Elm%20Ergonomic%20Side%20Sleeper%20pillow%20and%20the%20Coop%20Sleep%20Goods%20Original%20Crescent%20pillow.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f8d1a9ab24bc0b23a190d7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Eli%20%26amp%3B%20Elm%20Ergonomic%20Side%20Sleeper%20pillow%20and%20the%20Coop%20Sleep%20Goods%20Original%20Crescent%20pillow.%3Cp%3EBronwyn%20Barnes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226333bf7c-65f1-47ba-8fde-abd01fbe772d%5C%22%3EWhy%20you%20can%20trust%20Business%20Insider's%20pillow%20reviews%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20everyone%20has%20the%20time%2C%20budget%2C%20or%20patience%20to%20test%20dozens%20of%20pillows%20to%20f