-new-features-hotel-booking-shopping-personal-assistant-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUber%20app%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20you're%20not%20alone.%20The%20company's%20CEO%20doesn't%20have%20a%20perfect%20score.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazing-life-of-uber-new-ceo-dara-khosrowshahi-2017-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDara%20Khosrowshahi%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20on%20Molly%20O'Shea's%20Sourcery%2C%20published%20Friday%2C%20that%20his%20Uber%20rating%20is%204.83.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20Uber%20rating%20is%20like%204.83%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CEO%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20gotta%20get%20to%204.9.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20a%20little%20under%20the%20average%20Uber%20rider%20rating%20of%204.89%2C%20according%20to%20a%20company%20blog.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUber%20has%20said%20that%20it%20gives%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Fhow-to-check-uber-rating%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eratings%20to%20drivers%20and%20riders%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20ensure%20safety%20and%20accountability%20on%20the%20platform.%20Users%20who%20receive%20a%20rating%20below%20a%20certain%20threshold%20risk%20being%20booted%20from%20the%20app%2C%20though%20the%20company%20doesn't%20specify%20the%20exact%20minimum%20rating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKhosrowshahi%20said%20he's%20taking%20a%20few%20steps%20to%20keep%20his%20ratings%20up%2C%20including%20meeting%20his%20car%20on%20time%20and%20asking%20his%20driver%20for%20permission%20to%20use%20the%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CEO%20said%20he's%20also%20a%20big%20tipper%3A%20%26quot%3BFor%20a%20%2430%20ride%2C%20I'll%20tip%2010%2C%2015%20bucks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20pro-tip%20he%20gave%20was%20not%20to%20slam%20the%20car%20door.%20Uber%2C%20on%20its%20company%20blog%2C%20also%20says%20to%20keep%20the%20car%20clean%20and%20ask%20the%20driver%20for%20permission%20if%20you%20need%20to%20eat%20or%20drink%20in%20the%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20the%20Uber%20boss%20apparently%20doesn't%20give%20Khosrowshahi%20a%20leg%20up%20%E2%80%94some%20drivers%20don't%20know%20it's%20the%20CEO%20in%20the%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHalf%20of%20them%20know%20who%20I%20am%2C%20and%20then%20we%20chat%20on%20how%20things%20are%20going%20and%20how%20we%20can%20improve%20the%20product.%20And%20then%20half%20of%20them%20kind%20of%20are%20doing%20their%20own%20thing%2C%20and%20then%20I%20do%20my%20own%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20all%20good.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20time%20Khosrowshahi%20shared%20his%20Uber%20score%20with%20CBS%20Sunday%20Morning%20in%202025%2C%20he%20said%20it%20was%204.81.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20we're%20seeing%20some%20improvement%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-rating-ceo-dara-khosrowshahi-how-to-get-higher-rating-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778370005000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ffbb34e1443b8dc48e3a0c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-rating-ceo-dara-khosrowshahi-how-to-get-higher-rating-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Uber%20CEO%20Dara%20Khosrowshahi%20said%20he%20has%20a%204.83%20rating%20on%20his%20app%2C%20an%20improvement%20from%20the%20last%20time%20he%20shared%20his%20rating.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lloydlee%40insider.com%20(Lloyd%20Lee)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian%20model's%20understated%20Met%20Gala%20debut%20revives%20debate%20on%20cultural%20representation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778368115000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F5f30%2Flive%2Faf6c0ee0-4ad5-11f1-941e-d3689d7c57f6.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc