3E%3Cli%3EKayla%20Mazza%20rents%20a%20room%20in%20Honey%20Donegan's%20home%20after%20working%20with%20a%20nonprofit%20arranging%20matches.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20pays%20a%20reduced%20rent%20of%20%24650%20to%20help%20with%20Donegan's%20finances%20and%20occasionally%20does%20chores.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%2031-year-old%20analyst%20and%20the%2077-year-old%20nanny%20get%20along%20well%20and%20enjoy%20sharing%20the%20space.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20interview%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20data%20analyst%20and%20systems%20manager%20Kayla%20Mazza%2C%2031%2C%20of%20Windsor%20County%2C%20Vermont.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20night%2C%20at%207%20p.m.%2C%20my%20housemate%2C%20Honey%20Donegan%2C%2077%2C%20and%20I%20sit%20down%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeopardy-champion-behind-the-scenes-facts-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewatch%20Jeopardy%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20her%20den.%20Friday%20night%20is%20often%20movie%20night.%20It's%20a%20lovely%20bonding%20experience%2C%20despite%20the%2046-year%20age%20gap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHoney%20and%20I%20first%20met%20in%20March%202023%2C%20but%20our%20friendship%20has%20gotten%20stronger%20by%20the%20day%20since%20I%20moved%20into%20her%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20months%20before%2C%20I'd%20landed%20a%20job%20at%20a%20nonprofit%20near%20Honey's%20town%2C%20an%20hour's%20commute%20from%20my%20parents'%20home%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fafrica.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Five-lived-in-new-england-my-whole-life-theres-one-town-in-this-region-i-swear-by%2Fwxcy1f8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWaterbury%2C%20Vermont%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I'd%20stayed%20there%20temporarily%20until%20I%20found%20my%20own%20accommodation%20nearer%20my%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20as%20soon%20as%20I%20started%20looking%2C%20I%20felt%20discouraged.%20There%20was%20a%20lack%20of%20affordable%20housing%20in%20the%20area.%20Renting%20a%20room%20in%20a%20house%20with%20four%20other%20people%20can%20easily%20cost%20over%20%241%2C000%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d9624889-f29f-44fb-87d8-ca032d612023%5C%22%3EGuests%20like%20me%20are%20not%20considered%20carers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20new%20job%20was%20at%20a%20nonprofit%2C%20and%20I'd%20taken%20a%20pay%20cut%20from%20my%20previous%20position.%20In%20most%20cases%2C%20I%20didn't%20even%20qualify%20as%20a%20tenant%20because%20I%20didn't%20earn%20the%20required%20amount%20under%20the%20lease.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20you%20live%20with%20someone%20from%20another%20generation%3F%20Please%20email%20Jane%20Ridley%20at%20jridley%40insider.com%20if%20you'd%20like%20to%20share%20your%20story.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3EA%20relative%20told%20me%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.homesharevermont.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHomeShare%20Vermont%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20nonprofit%20that%20matches%20older%20people%20with%20empty%20space%20in%20their%20homes%20with%20people%20like%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20an%20arrangement%20that%20works%20financially%20for%20both%20the%20guest%20and%20the%20host.%20As%20well%20as%20companionship%2C%20the%20host's%20incentives%20include%20the%20guest%20often%20assisting%20with%20chores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGuests%20are%20not%20considered%20carers%2C%20but%20they%20may%20help%20with%20tasks%20such%20as%20cooking%20meals%2C%20grocery%20shopping%2C%20and%20rides%20to%20the%20doctor's%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224128%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20younger%20and%20older%20woman%20sitting%20on%20a%20sofa%20with%20a%20dog.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fe293ae1443b8dc48e358a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223096%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMazza%20and%20Donegan%20with%20Tinker%2C%20one%20of%20Donegan's%20two%20dogs.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Kayla%20Mazza.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20party%20is%20vetted%20by%20the%20organization%2C%20and%20I%20was%20excited%20to%20be%20matched%20with%20Honey%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprofessional-nanny-longs-to-help-care-for-her-grandchildren-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epart-time%20nanny%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20a%20four-bedroom%20house%20in%20a%20homeowners'%20association.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20settled%20on%20a%20reasonable%20rent%20of%20%24650%20a%20month%20%E2%80%94%20the%20maximum%20HomeShare%20allows%20for%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Favoided-assisted-living-housemates-aging-in-place-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshared-housing%20arrangement%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%94%20plus%20a%20percentage%20of%C2%A0utilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20rent%20was%20higher%20than%20the%20average%20%24380%20monthly%20amount%20that%20HomeShare%20guests%20pay%2C%20mainly%20because%20Honey's%20needs%20were%20few.%20Some%20living%20situations%20are%20more%20intensive%20and%20may%20require%20a%20nightly%20presence%20and%20a%20set%20number%20of%20hours%20of%20assistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2257901ad7-e3a5-4007-91e0-dbd41ccc40b5%5C%22%3EThe%20expectations%20were%20set%20in%20advance%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20worked%20out%20really%20well%20because%20I%20have%20a%20full-time%20job%20and%20am%20very%20busy.%20I%20also%20like%20visiting%20family%20and%20traveling%20a%20lot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Honey%20is%20the%20most%20active%20senior%20I%20know%2C%20especially%20since%20she%20has%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20little%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20expectations%20were%20discussed%20in%20advance%20of%20what%20I%20should%20help%20with%2C%20such%20as%20watching%20her%20pets%20%E2%80%94%20two%20cats%2C%20two%20dogs%2C%20and%20some%20fish%20%E2%80%94%20when%20she's%20away%20or%20stacking%20wood%20in%20the%20winter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20really%20clicked%20and%20have%20never%20needed%20HomeShare's%20mediation%20if%20problems%20ever%20arise%20between%20housemates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c17b29e6-08e4-46ea-9882-2bedd7a61f8a%5C%22%3EWe're%20both%20avid%20readers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20liking%20Jeopardy%20and%20funny%20movies%2C%20we%20have%20other%20things%20in%20common.%20We%20hike%20together%2C%20walk%20the%20dogs%2C%20and%20swim%20at%20a%20nearby%20lake.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20similar%20political%20beliefs%20and%20are%20both%20avid%20readers.%20Honey%2C%20who%20is%20extremely%20empathetic%2C%20would%20never%20judge%20me%20for%20curling%20up%20with%20a%20book%20for%20an%20entire%20weekend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20we%20have%20open%20conversations%20about%20coming%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-goes-vacation-twice-year-grandparents-pick-up-the-tab-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edifferent%20generations%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20arrangement%20makes%20good%20financial%20sense%2C%20and%20it's%20stimulating%20and%20rewarding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fintergenerational-home-sharing-friendship-vermont-cost-living-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778352541000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fcf8c8e1443b8dc48e2ffc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fintergenerational-home-sharing-friendship-vermont-cost-living-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kayla%20Mazza%2C%2031%2C%20pays%20a%20reduced%20rent%20to%20housemate%20Honey%20Donegan%2C%2077%2C%20in%20return%20for%20companionship%20and%20doing%20odd%20chores.%20It%20works%20well%20for%20both%20women.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Jane%20Ridley)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Russia%20grateful%20to%20US%20for%20talks'%3A%20Putin%20say