tavirus%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20evacuate%20early%20Sunday%20morning.%20Some%20Tenerife%20residents%20have%20protested%20the%20ship's%20scheduled%20arrival%2C%20concerned%20that%20it%20could%20cause%20another%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20you%20are%20worried.%20I%20know%20that%20when%20you%20hear%20the%20word%20'outbreak'%20and%20watch%20a%20ship%20sail%20toward%20your%20shores%2C%20memories%20surface%20that%20none%20of%20us%20have%20fully%20put%20to%20rest%2C%26quot%3B%20Ghebreyesus%20said%20on%20Saturday.%20%26quot%3BThe%20pain%20of%202020%20is%20still%20real%2C%20and%20I%20do%20not%20dismiss%20it%20for%20a%20single%20moment.%20But%20I%20need%20you%20to%20hear%20me%20clearly%3A%20this%20is%20not%20another%20COVID-19.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ETo%20the%20people%20of%20Tenerife%2C%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EMy%20name%20is%20Tedros%2C%20and%20I%20serve%20as%20the%20Director-General%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FWHO%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40WHO%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUN%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40UN%3C%2Fa%3E%20agency%20responsible%20for%20global%20public%20health.%20It%20is%20not%20common%20for%20me%20to%20write%20directly%20to%20the%20people%20of%20a%20single%20community%2C%20but%20today%20I%20feel%20it%20is%20not%20only%20appropriate%2C%20it%20is%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Flx05ji4a79%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Flx05ji4a79%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Tedros%20Adhanom%20Ghebreyesus%20(%40DrTedros)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDrTedros%2Fstatus%2F2053083645292773817%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%209%2C%202026%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EGhebreyesus%20said%20the%20current%20public%20health%20risk%20from%20hantavirus%20remains%20low%2C%20and%20there%20are%20no%20symptomatic%20passengers%20aboard%20the%20ship%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcruise-ship-atlantic-viral-outbreak-deaths-hantavirus-world-health-organization-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecalled%20the%20MV%20Honduis%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20at%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSpain's%20authorities%20have%20prepared%20a%20careful%2C%20step-by-step%20plan%3A%20passengers%20will%20be%20ferried%20ashore%20at%20the%20industrial%20port%20of%20Granadilla%2C%20far%20from%20residential%20areas%2C%20in%20sealed%2C%20guarded%20vehicles%2C%20through%20a%20completely%20cordoned-off%20corridor%2C%20and%20repatriated%20directly%20to%20their%20home%20countries%2C%26quot%3B%20Ghebreyesus%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20will%20not%20encounter%20them.%20Your%20families%20will%20not%20encounter%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Protests%20about%20hantavirus%20cruise%20ship%20docking%20in%20Tenerife.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ff5e2be1443b8dc48e39b5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESome%20Tenerife%20residents%20protested%20the%20scheduled%20arrival%20of%20the%20cruise%20ship.%3Cp%3EJORGE%20GUERRERO%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20World%20Health%20Organization%20first%20received%20reports%20of%20passengers%20with%20severe%20respiratory%20illness%20aboard%20the%20cruise%20ship%20on%20May%202.%20As%20of%20May%208%2C%20a%20total%20of%20eight%20cases%2C%20including%20three%20deaths%2C%20have%20been%20reported.%20Health%20officials%20said%20the%20virus%20is%20the%20Andes%20strain%2C%20known%20to%20have%20limited%20human-to-human%20transmission.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%2C%20which%20officially%20withdrew%20from%20the%20World%20Health%20Organization%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20shared%20an%20update%20for%20Americans%20through%20the%20Centers%20for%20Disease%20Control%20and%20Prevention%20on%20May%208.%20At%20the%20moment%2C%20the%20risk%20to%20the%20American%20public%20and%20travelers%20%26quot%3Bremains%20extremely%20low%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20agency%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20X%20post%2C%20Ghebreyesus%20thanked%20Prime%20Minister%20Pedro%20S%C3%A1nchez%20of%20Spain%20for%20agreeing%20to%20receive%20the%20cruise%20ship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20intend%20to%20travel%20to%20Tenerife%20to%20observe%20this%20operation%20firsthand%2C%20to%20stand%20alongside%20the%20health%20workers%2C%20port%20staff%2C%20and%20officials%20who%20are%20making%20it%20happen%2C%20and%20to%20personally%20pay%20my%20respects%20to%20an%20island%20that%20has%20responded%20to%20a%20difficult%20situation%20with%20grace%2C%20solidarity%2C%20and%20compassion.%20Your%20humanity%20deserves%20to%20be%20witnessed%2C%20not%20just%20acknowledged%20from%20a%20distance%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGhebreyesus%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BAs%20I%20have%20said%20many%20times%3A%20viruses%20do%20not%20care%20about%20politics%2C%20and%20they%20do%20not%20respect%20borders.%20The%20best%20immunity%20any%20of%20us%20has%20is%20solidarity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhantavirus-outbreak-not-another-covid-19-pandemic-cruise-ship-who-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778345196000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ff5f5cc9dd4cb81cda8e7c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhantavirus-outbreak-not-another-covid-19-pandemic-cruise-ship-who-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20World%20Health%20Organization%20said%20eight%20cases%20of%20hantavirus%2C%20including%20three%20deaths%2C%20have%20been%20rep