0I%20assumed%20I'd%20be%20able%20to%20use%20credit%20cards%20and%20easily%20get%20cash.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EUnfortunately%2C%20ATM%20fees%20and%20credit-card%20charges%20were%20quite%20high%20on%20the%20islands.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENext%20time%2C%20I'll%20bring%20more%20cash%20and%20spend%20more%20time%20in%20the%20Gal%C3%A1pagos%20to%20help%20my%20money%20go%20further.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20I%20took%20a%20dream%20vacation%20to%20a%20place%20I%20had%20heard%20about%20my%20whole%20life%2C%20but%20never%20thought%20I%20would%20have%20the%20chance%20to%20visit%3A%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-to-do-on-the-galpagos-islands-according-to-frequent-visitor%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGal%C3%A1pagos%20Islands%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20swam%20with%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-marine-life-can-reduce-our-plastic-consumption-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20sea%20turtles%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20sharks%2C%20hung%20out%20with%20sea%20lions%2C%20and%20walked%20with%20the%20legendary%20giant%20tortoises.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20traveled%20solo%2C%20skipped%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-i-hate-about-cruises-from-frequent-cruiser-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etouristy%20cruises%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20flew%20coach%2C%20and%20negotiated%20for%20some%20great%20deals%2C%20but%20my%20trip%20was%20nearly%20overshadowed%20by%20one%20major%20mistake%3A%20I%20didn't%20bring%20nearly%20enough%20cold%2C%20hard%20cash%20in%20the%20form%20of%20US%20dollars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEcuador%20is%20a%20fully%20dollarized%20economy%2C%20which%20means%20American%20travelers%20don't%20even%20need%20to%20exchange%20currency.%20However%2C%20getting%20dollars%20once%20I%20was%20on%20the%20islands%20proved%20to%20be%20more%20difficult%20%E2%80%94%20and%20expensive%20%E2%80%94%20than%20I%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2282503e81-2556-4d37-bac8-aa9cf23c9d0e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlthough%20I%20brought%20some%20cash%2C%20I%20spent%20most%20of%20it%20before%20my%20vacation%20even%20began%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22People%20walking%20through%20entrance%20of%20acvitity%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f265fe3a8599320969e780%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20didn't%20get%20nearly%20enough%20cash%20in%20Ecuador%20before%20I%20headed%20to%20the%20islands.%3Cp%3EDion%20Rabouin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20my%20trip%2C%20I%20thought%20a%20few%20hundred%20dollars%20would%20be%20all%20I%20needed%20for%20the%20week.%20Instead%2C%20my%20cash%20was%20gone%20before%20I%20even%20saw%20a%20blue-footed%20booby.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20one%2C%20there's%20a%20long%20list%20of%20fees%20visitors%20have%20to%20pay%20just%20to%20enter%20the%20islands.%20There%20are%20also%20costs%20to%20get%20from%20the%20mostly%20uninhabited%20island%20where%20the%20main%20airport%20is%20located%20to%20other%20islands%2C%20where%20it's%20actually%20possible%20to%20book%20a%20stay%20for%20the%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20I%20spent%20%2420%20on%20a%20Gal%C3%A1pagos%20Transit%20Control%20Card%20at%20the%20mainland%20airport%20in%20Guayaquil%2C%20Ecuador.%20This%20is%20a%20mandatory%20document%20for%20all%20visitors%2C%20used%20to%20monitor%20tourism%20and%20manage%20immigration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20I%20flew%20to%20the%20Seymour%20Airport%2C%20located%20on%20the%20mostly%20uninhabited%20island%20of%20Baltra%20in%20the%20Gal%C3%A1pagos.%20I%20paid%20a%20%24200%20mandatory%20national-park%20entry%20fee%20so%20I%20could%20exit%20the%20airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Interior%20of%20bus%20with%20colofrul%20seats%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f265fe402f8423cd99c106%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20took%20several%20forms%20of%20transportation%20to%20reach%20my%20accommodations.%3Cp%3EDion%20Rabouin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20there%2C%20I%20spent%20about%20%2415%20to%20take%20a%20bus%20and%20ferry%20from%20Baltra%20to%20Santa%20Cruz%2C%20where%20my%20accommodations%20and%20tours%20were%20located.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20I%20arrived%20in%20Santa%20Cruz%2C%20I%20paid%20%2425%20for%20a%20taxi%20from%20the%20ferry%20terminal%20to%20the%20main%20town.%20I%20would've%20just%20taken%20the%20bus%20for%20about%20%245%2C%20but%20none%20were%20available%20when%20I%20arrived.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fab69783-6b49-47df-98d9-a851a4b42a07%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EUsing%20credit%20cards%20and%20getting%20cash%20on%20the%20islands%20wasn't%20as%20great%20or%20as%20easy%20as%20I'd%20anticipated%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22View%20of%20water%20in%20Galapgos%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f265fe45d547f1b7ed34ef%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUsing%20my%20credit%20card%20got%20expensive.%3Cp%3EDion%20Rabouin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20I%20didn't%20have%20much%20cash%20by%20the%20time%20I%20arrived%20at%20my%20accommodations%2C%20I%20still%20had%20my%20credit%20cards%20and%20knew%20I'd%20be%20able%20to%20withdraw%20US%20dollars%20from%20any%20ATM%20in%20the%20country%20if%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20I%20found%20out%20too%20late%20that%20many%20locally%20owned%20accommodations%20won't%20accept%20credit%20cards%2C%20and%20almost%20all%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-tours-by-locals-review-best-way-to-travel-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elocal%20tour%20operators%3C%2Fa%3E%20charge%20hefty%20fees%20for%20using%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOperators%20tack%20on%20credit-card%20or%20%26quot%3Bconvenience%26quot%3B%20fees%20that%20can%20rise%20to%20as%20high%20as%2010%25%20or%2020%25%20of%20the%20total%20bill.%20When%20I%20started%20really%20running%20low%20on%20money%2C%20I%20learned%20that%20convenience%20comes%20at%20a%20steep%20price%20for%20cash%2C%20too.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBetween%20the%20local%20ATM%20fees%20and%20my%20bank's%20international%20and%20out-of-network%20charges%2C%20I%20got%20hit%20with%20more%20than%20%2425%20in%20fees%20on%20a%20single%20withdrawal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2285a62264-464f-4dda-8ae3-6f685711d350%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELooking%20back%2C%20there%20are%20a%20few%20ways%20I%20wish%20I'd%20saved%20money%20on%20my%20trip%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Man%20posing%20with%20turtle%20in%20galapagos%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f265fe45d547f1b7ed34f1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEven%20if%20I%20hadn't%20brought%20more%20cash%20from%20home%2C%20I%20should've%20at%20least%20gotten%20it%20before%20flying%20to%20the%20Gal%C3%A1pagos%20Islands.%3Cp%3EDion%20Rabouin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20planning%20your%20first%20trip%2C%20don't%20follow%20in%20my%20footsteps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%20of%20all%2C%20a%20shorter%20stay%20offers%20the%20least%20bang%20for%20your%20buck%2C%20and%20my%20trip%20was%20just%20three%20days.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20upfront%20fees%20to%20enter%20the%20islands%20are%20the%20same%20regardless%20of%20how%20long%20you're%20staying%2C%20my%20cost-per-day%20breakdown%20felt%20astronomical.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20going%20to%20pay%20the%20price%20of%20admission%20to%20the%20islands%2C%20I%20suggest%20you%20stay%20at%20least%20a%20week%20to%20make%20the%20initial%20investment%20worth%20it.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bird%20on%20rocks%20in%20galapagos%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f265fe3a8599320969e782%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIf%20I%20could%20do%20this%20trip%20over%2C%20I'd%20spend%20more%20time%20in%20the%20Gal%C3%A1pagos.%3Cp%3EDion%20Rabouin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20weeklong%20stay%2C%20I'd%20also%20advise%20packing%20at%20least%20%24600%20in%20a%20mix%20of%20bills%20ranging%20from%20%245%20to%20%24100%20so%20you%20can%20tip%20easily%20without%20worrying%20about%20getting%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20bringing%20more%20cash%20from%20home%20isn't%20feasible%2C%20it's%20at%20least%20worth%20withdrawing%20some%20before%20flying%20to%20the%20Gal%C3%A1pagos.%20Major%20cities%20like%20Guayaquil%20and%20Quito%2C%20where%20most%20visitors%20catch%20their%20flights%20to%20the%20islands%2C%20tend%20to%20have%20lower%20ATM%20fees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20in%20all%2C%20I%20had%20a%20great%20time%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgalapagos-islands-photos-2012-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eseeing%20the%20Gal%C3%A1pagos%20Islands%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20my%20vacation%20could've%20gone%20smoother%20%E2%80%94%20and%20been%20a%20better%20value%20%E2%80%94%20if%20I'd%20been%20a%20bit%20more%20prepared.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-money-mistake-trip-galapagos-islands-how-to-avoid-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778342761000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f265fe45d547f1b7ed34f0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-money-mistake-trip-galapagos-islands-how-to-avoid-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Not%20packing%20enough%20cash%20cost%20me%20time%20and%20money%20during%20my%20dream%20bucket-list%20trip%20to%20the%20Galapagos%20Islands.%20Here's%20what%20I'll%20do%20differently%20next%20time.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Dion%20Rabouin)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canoni