%20option%20to%20order%20a%20beverage%20or%20snack%20along%20with%20an%20Uber%20Black%20ride%2C%20or%20to%20have%20a%20courier%20buy%20something%20on%20your%20behalf%20at%20a%20local%20mom-and-pop%20store.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20March%2C%20the%20company%20rolled%20out%20Uber%20Elite%2C%20an%20invite-only%20ride%20service%20that%20uses%20professional%20drivers%20and%20luxury%20vehicles%20to%20cater%20to%20business%20and%20other%20high-paying%20travelers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlack%20car%20rides%20and%20other%20%26quot%3Bhigh-value%20modes%26quot%3B%20have%20been%20a%20focus%20for%20Lyft%20as%20well%20over%20the%20last%20few%20quarters%2C%20CEO%20David%20Risher%20said%20on%20the%20company's%20earnings%20call%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDoorDash%20also%20gained%20traction%20last%20year%20among%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboomers-are-giving-doordash-a-boost-new-data-shows-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebaby%20boomers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20data%20from%20polling%20firm%20Morning%20Consult%20found.%20This%20generation%20tends%20to%20have%20more%20wealth%2C%20including%20disposable%20income%2C%20than%20younger%20generations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220162e01f-a1e4-4f77-83ac-8061f3d051fc%5C%22%3EA%20'barbell'%20strategy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20everything%20the%20apps%20are%20doing%20is%20aimed%20at%20affluent%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstacart%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20found%20that%20retailers%20that%20offer%20the%20same%20prices%20on%20its%20app%20as%20in%20their%20stores%20perform%20better%20than%20those%20that%20mark%20up%20their%20prices%2C%20CEO%20Chris%20Rogers%20said%20on%20a%20Wednesday%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCustomers%20are%20seeking%20value%2C%20and%20the%20retailers%20on%20our%20platform%20who%20are%20delivering%20it%2C%20they're%20growing%20faster%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUber%20CEO%20Khosrowshahi%20has%20said%20that%20his%20company%20uses%20a%20%26quot%3Bbarbell%26quot%3B%20strategy%20%E2%80%94%20one%20that%20caters%20to%20both%20customers%20trying%20to%20save%20money%20and%20those%20with%20more%20to%20spend.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20some%20cost-conscious%20customers%20use%20the%20app%20as%20an%20alternative%20to%20car%20ownership%2C%20Mulberry%20said%2C%20a%20pitch%20that%20Uber%20and%20Lyft%20have%20been%20making%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20users%2C%20Uber%20looks%20more%20like%20a%20utility%20than%20the%20source%20for%20%26quot%3Ba%20discretionary%20ride%20from%20time%20to%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20Uber%2C%20DoorDash%2C%20or%20another%20ride-hailing%20service%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aabitter%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eabitter%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20via%20encrypted%20messaging%20app%20Signal%20at%20808-854-4501.%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%2C%20a%20nonwork%20WiFi%20network%2C%20and%20a%20nonwork%20device%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehere's%20our%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-guide-to-securely-sharing-whistleblower-information-about-powerful-institutions-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eguide%20to%20sharing%20information%20securely%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-doordash-boost-earnings-with-high-income-users-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778332739000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fb8e40e1443b8dc48e2796%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-doordash-boost-earnings-with-high-income-users-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Uber%2C%20DoorDash%2C%20and%20Instacart%20are%20targeting%20high-income%20consumers%20with%20premium%20services%2C%20lifting%20their%20quarterly%20earnings%20and%20stock%20prices.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22abitter%40businessinsider.com%20(Alex%20Bitter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20took%20my%20kids%20%E2%80%94%20all%20under%208%20%E2%80%94%20to%20Epic%20Universe.%20Here%20are%205%20things%20that%20made%20our%20visit%20a%20total%20success.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20a%20Epic%20Universe%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69efa41e367066d7c2971920%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223213%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20visited%20Super%20Nintendo%20World%20in%20Orlando.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMy%20three%20kids%2C%20all%20under%208%2C%20are%20obsessed%20with%20Super%20Mario%20Bros.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDuring%20a%20recent%20trip%20to%20Florida%2C%20we%20visited%20Epic%20Universe%20in%20Orlando.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGetting%20Express%20Passes%20was%20key%20to%20riding%20all%20the%20rides%20we%20wanted.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20three%20kids%20are%208%2C%206%2C%20and%206%2C%20and%20totally%20obsessed%20with%20Mario%20and%20his%20friends.%20We've%20watched%20both%20movies%20multiple%20times%2C%20played%20Super%20Mario%20Bros.%20on%20several%20gaming%20systems%2C%20and%20have%20plenty%20of%20stuffed%20toys%20of%20each%20character.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20taken%20my%20oldest%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpaid-extra-early-entrance-universal-super-nintendo-world-worth-it-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESuper%20Nintendo%20World%20in%20California%3C%2Fa%3E%20years%20ago%2C%20but%20now%20that%20my%20twins%20are%20older%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20take%20them%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20recent%20trip%20to%20Florida%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20stop%20in%20Orlando%20for%2024%20hours%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvisited-universal-new-theme-park-epic-universe-highlights-disappointments-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Evisit%20Epic%20Universe%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Here%20are%20five%20things%20that%20made%20our%20trip%20a%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2269c0fdca-873e-4c6d-bd29-d48486843ee3%5C%22%3EWe%20had%20early%20entrance%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20stay%20at%20Universal%20resorts%2C%20you%20can%20enter%20their%20four%20parks%20an%20hour%20before%20everyone%20else.%20We%20chose%20to%20stay%20at%20Surfside%20Inn%20not%20just%20because%20of%20the%20early%20entrance%20perk%20but%20also%20because%20you%20can%20take%20a%20shuttle%20to%20and%20from%20the%20parks%2C%20and%20forget%20about%20having%20to%20park%20your%20car%20(a%20big%20savings).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20early%20entrance%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20key.%20We%20took%20the%20shuttle%20a%20little%20before%208%20a.m.%20and%20were%20in%20line%20exactly%20an%20hour%20before%20the%20park%20opened.%20We%20took%20that%20time%20to%20apply%20sunscreen%2C%20finish%20snacks%2C%20and%20get%20ready%20to%20have%20fun.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22People%20lining%20up%20to%20enter%20park.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f0a3aea98bc8fdc096f900%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223213%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20early%20entrance%20at%20Epic%20Universe%20in%20Orlando.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20ready%20by%20the%20Super%20Nintendo%20World%20entrance%20at%208%3A45%20a.m.%2C%20where%20we%20needed%20to%20show%20our%20room%20keys%20to%20be%20allowed%20in.%20At%20exactly%209%20a.m.%2C%20we%20stepped%20into%20the%20pipe%20portal%20that%20took%20us%20to%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20early%20entrance%20was%20key%20to%20riding%20all%20the%20rides%20at%20Super%20Nintendo%20World%20without%20waiting%20in%20line.%20We%20were%20then%20able%20to%20walk%20over%20to%20the%20Isle%20of%20Berk%20(the%20world%20for%20%26quot%3BHow%20to%20Train%20Your%20Dragon%26quot%3B)%20and%20do%20all%20the%20rides%20there%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bdb28e10-de7a-4160-8f26-7fce557f4d90%5C%22%3EExpress%20passes%20were%20key%20to%20riding%20everything%20we%20wanted%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPark%20tickets%20start%20at%20%24139%20for%20adults%20and%20%24134%20for%20kids%20under%209.%20Those%20tickets%20allow%20you%20to%20use%20the%20regular%20line%20for%20all%20rides%2C%20but%20we%20decided%20to%20get%20Express%20passes%20to%20make%20the%20most%20of%20our%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Family%20meeting%20Toothless%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f0a7b7367066d7c2971c67%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223213%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECharacter%20meet-ups%20do%20not%20have%20express%20passes%20and%2C%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20can%20have%20long%20waits.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EExpress%20passes%20are%20%24199.99%20each%20for%20Epic%20Universe%2C%20which%20is%20definitely%20a%20splurge.%20But%2C%20for%20example%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fharry-potter-rides-universal-orlando-ranked-2019-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHarry%20Potter%20ride%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20a%20wait%20time%20of%20over%20300%20minutes%20during%20our%20visit%2C%20and%20with%20the%20express%20pass%2C%20we%20did%20it%20in%20less%20than%2020.%20Had%20we%20stayed%20in%20the%20regular%20line%2C%20between%20that%20wait%20and%20other%20rides%2C%20we%20would've%20only%20been%20able%20to%20do%20maybe%20two%20or%20three%20in%20total.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECharacter%20meet-ups%20do%20not%20have%20fast%20passes%2C%20so%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvisited-universal-epic-universe-theme-park-photos-review-value-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elongest%20waits%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20for%20those.%20To%20see%20Toothless%2C%20the%20line%20said%2080%20minutes%2C%20but%20we%20waited%20more%20like%2045.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b545143b-e076-4290-adbb-b0275266367e%5C%22%3ESome%20worlds%20are%20so%20hot%2C%20so%20we%20planned%20around%20that%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20Orlando%20in%20April%20is%20going%20to%20be%20hot%2C%20but%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fepic-universe-review-photos-food-theme-park-universal-orlando-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epark%20can%20get%20really%20hot%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20some%20areas%2C%20so%20be%20prepared%20to%20keep%20kids%20hydrated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mom%20walking%20with%20child%20through%20Epic%20Universe%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f0a632a98bc8fdc096f918%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223213%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Super%20Nintendo%20World%20had%20very%20little%20shade.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESuper%20Nintendo%20World%20was%20scorching%20during%20our%20visit.%20There%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funiversal-new-theme-park-problem-epic-universe-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Every%20little%20shade%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20similar%20to%20the%20experience%20of%20the%20world%20in%20the%20California%20park%20%E2%80%94%20but%20you%20are%20also%20enclosed%20by%20the%20castle's%20walls%2C%20so%20there's%20absolutely%20no%20breeze.%20We%20skipped%20waiting%20in%20line%20to%20meet%20the%20characters%20(something%20my%20kids%20wanted%20to%20do)%20because%20we%20would've%20had%20to%20stand%20in%20the%20midday%20sun%20for%2030%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20mixed%20in%20water%20rides%20midway%20through%20the%20day%20to%20cool%20down%2C%20and%20we%20chose%20to%20sit%20down%20inside%20for%20lunch%20to%20take%20a%20break%20from%20the%20sun.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2251afda7d-92ca-4a6c-8df4-82547a2ae198%5C%22%3EKeep%20an%20eye%20on%20rides%20to%20manage%20big%20emotions%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20downloaded%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funiversal-epic-universe-disney-world-competition-florida-economy-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUniversal%20Orlando%20app%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20we%20were%20waiting%20in%20line%20for%20early%20entrance.%20It%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20key%20because%20we%20could%20check%20wait%20times%20%3Cmark%20data-color%3D%5C%22%239efcf6%5C%22%3Ef%3C%2Fmark%3Eor%20rides%20and%20activities%20throughout%20the%20day%20to%20plan%20where%20to%20go%20next.%20On%20top%20of%20that%2C%20we%20could%20also%20check%20if%20attractions%20were%20running.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Toad%20merch%20at%20Epic%20Universal%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f0a9baa98bc8fdc096f930%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223213%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPrices%20of%20merch%20ranged%20from%20%2422%20for%20a%20small%20stuffie%20to%20%2479%20for%20a%20hoodie.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20kids%20were%20so%20incredibly%20bummed%20that%20the%20Yoshi's%20Adventure%20ride%20was%20closed%20the%20day%20of%20our%20visit%2C%20and%20they%20could%20not%20ride%20it%20at%20all.%20It%20was%20one%20that%20they%20were%20looking%20forward%20to%20ahead%20of%20our%20trip.%20Obviously%2C%20things%20like%20this%20are%20out%20of%20our%20control%2C%20but%20knowing%20before%20we%20made%20it%20all%20the%20way%20to%20the%20ride%20helped%20us%20talk%20to%20our%20kids%20and%20prepare%20them%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20tried%20to%20ride%20the%20Donkey%20Kong%20Mine%20Cart%20Madness%20ride%20twice%2C%20but%20the%20second%20time%2C%20while%20we%20were%20in%20line%2C%20the%20ride%20broke%20down.%20We%20waited%2010%20minutes%2C%20and%20when%20we%20realized%20there%20wasn't%20much%20improvement%20on%20the%20line%2C%20we%20left%20and%20did%20other%20things%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221c7c1786-e06a-497b-b42d-6cff83efba53%5C%22%3EIt's%20an%20expensive%20experience%2C%20but%20we%20leaned%20into%20it%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20surprises%20here.%20Between%20park%20tickets%2C%20express%20passes%2C%20and%20souvenirs%2C%20the%20whole%20day%20can%20be%20really%20expensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20surprised%20to%20see%20hoodies%20retailing%20for%20%2479%2C%20so%20I%20skipped%20them.%20But%20I%20couldn't%20leave%20the%20park%20without%20buying%20each%20of%20my%20kids%20the%20smallest%20stuffed%20animal%20I%20could%20find%2C%20costing%20%2422%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mario%20Burger%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f0a88f367066d7c2971c70%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20got%20a%20Mario%20burger%20at%20Toadstool%20caf%C3%A9.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20still%20leaned%20into%20saying%20yes%20to%20many%20things.%20My%20kids%20wanted%20to%20meet%20Toothless%2C%20and%20despite%20the%20long%20line%2C%20we%20agreed%20because%20it's%20one%20of%20their%20favorite%20characters.%20They%20also%20wanted%20to%20eat%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funiversal-epic-universe-theme-park-food-first-look-photos-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EToadstool%20Caf%C3%A9%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20while%20I%20knew%20it%20would%20be%20overstimulating%20for%20everyone%2C%20we%20took%20it%20as%20a%20chance%20to%20take%20a%20break%2C%20sit%20down%2C%20and%20let%20everyone%20get%20some%20energy%20and%20calories%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fepic-universe-orlando-family-trip-tips-what-worked-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778332561000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69efa5c43fecbb42897a4a10%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fepic-universe-orlando-family-trip-tips-what-worked-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20took%20my%20three%20kids%20to%20Epic%20Universe%20for%20a%20day%20and%20learned%20what's%20worth%20the%20splurge%20%E2%80%94%20and%20what%20to%20plan%20for.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cpreti%40insider.com%20(Conz%20Preti)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20moved%20back%20in%20with%20my%20parents%20at%2024.%20It%20made%20me%20grow%20up%20way%20more%20than%20renting%20with%20friends.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20packs%20up%20the%20contents%20of%20her%20apartment%20before%20moving%20back%20in%20with%20her%20parents.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fc8284c9dd4cb81cda8040%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22841%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%2C%20shown%20packing%20up%20her%20apartment%2C%20said%20that%20she%20was%20initially%20embarrassed%20about%20moving%20back%20in%20with%20her%20parents.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Eliza%20Pepper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20negative%20discourse%20around%20adult%20children%20moving%20back%20in%20with%20their%20parents.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20made%20the%20move%20last%20year%2C%20after%20my%20mom%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20cancer.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI've%20grown%20up%20more%20over%20the%20past%20few%20months%20living%20at%20home%20than%20I%20did%20while%20renting.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20fall%2C%20I%20felt%20like%20a%20picture%20of%20success%20in%20my%2020s.%20I%20was%20developing%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvaluable-lessons-to-learn-in-your-first-job-2015-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efast-paced%20career%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20living%20in%20central%20London%20with%20friends%2C%20and%20had%20just%20enough%20time%20and%20money%20to%20enjoy%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20the%20life%20I'd%20built%20collapsed.%20In%20quick%20succession%2C%20my%20mum%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20cancer%2C%20and%20my%20grandfather%20suffered%20a%20debilitating%20stroke.%20While%20friends%20continued%20with%20the%20cycle%20of%20work%20and%20socials%2C%20I%20was%20shocked%20into%20pausing%20mine%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboomerang-kids-moving-back-in-with-parents-saving-money-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emove%20back%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20with%20my%20parents%20at%2024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENothing%20could%20make%20me%20trade%20being%20with%20my%20family%20during%20this%20crisis%2C%20so%20why%20did%20I%20feel%20embarrassed%20admitting%20I%20lived%20at%20home%20to%20acquaintances%20or%20colleagues%20who%20didn't%20have%20the%20context%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEverywhere%20I%20looked%2C%20there%20was%20a%20narrative%20that%20adults%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-moved-back-home-several-times-boomerang-child-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elive%20with%20their%20parents%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20regressive%20dependents%2C%20resented%20by%20their%20families.%20That%20certainly%20doesn't%20fit%20my%20situation%2C%20and%20it%20can't%20possibly%20apply%20to%20the%20majority%20of%20Gen%20Zers%2C%20who%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20live%20with%20their%20parents%20than%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcls.ucl.ac.uk%2Fgen-z-more-likely-to-live-with-parents-in-early-20s-than-previous-generations%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eearlier%20generations%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a9e505bd-2855-4e69-b10c-8f81ea445c1e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDefining%20%26quot%3Badulthood%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20felt%20%26quot%3Badult%26quot%3B%20when%20I%20first%20moved%20out%2C%20but%20looking%20back%2C%20it%20was%20permission%20to%20be%20immature.%20The%20logistics%20were%20easy%2C%20I%20could%20do%20whatever%20I%20wanted%2C%20and%20my%20greatest%20commitment%20was%20making%20rent%20each%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222049%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20and%20her%20family%20look%20over%20a%20cliff.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fc852de1443b8dc48e2b72%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221537%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%2C%20who%20recently%20moved%20home%20to%20help%20care%20for%20her%20parents%2C%20says%20she%20enjoys%20getting%20to%20know%20them%20as%20an%20adult.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Eliza%20Pepper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20faced%20a%20family%20crisis%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcaregiving-balance-full-time-job-caring-for-mom-teens-family-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecaregiving%20responsibilities%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20can%20firmly%20say%20I'm%20much%20more%20grown-up%20now.%20Many%20adult%20children%20living%20with%20parents%20will%20have%20learned%20similar%20adult%20lessons%2C%20whether%20they've%20boomeranged%20home%20for%20a%20career%20break%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffollowed-partner-to-new-york-broke-up-went-home-atlanta-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eafter%20a%20breakup%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EI%20also%20have%20greater%20responsibilities%20at%20home%20than%20I%20ever%20did%20as%20a%20tenant.%20Though%20I%20initially%20struggled%20with%20the%20shock%20of%20the%20situation%20and%20my%20increased%20commitments%2C%20handling%20challenges%20as%20part%20of%20a%20family%20unit%20is%20probably%20more%20representative%20of%20my%20future%20adult%20life%20which%20will%20likely%20incluvde%20mortgages%2C%20childcare%2C%20and%20any%20other%20curveballs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20circumstances%20are%20rare%2C%20with%20the%20majority%20of%20Gen-Z%20living%20at%20home%20for%20financial%20reasons%20like%20volatile%20income%2C%20unaffordable%20rent%2C%20and%20saving%20to%20get%20on%20the%20property%20ladder.%20Still%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20it's%20right%20that%20my%20peers%20are%20labeled%20as%20childish%20for%20living%20with%20their%20parents%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20more%20mature%20than%20the%20alternative%20of%20debt%20or%20relying%20on%20family%20to%20bail%20you%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20sometimes%20think%20landlords%2C%20perhaps%2C%20are%20the%20main%20group%20benefiting%20from%20the%20belief%20that%20adults%20move%20out%20of%20the%20family%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b2893d0e-9f66-4142-b7d3-db23fb215937%5C%22%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cstrong%3EAging%20goes%20both%20ways%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20what%20I've%20seen%2C%20the%20current%20conversation%20focuses%20only%20on%20the%20right%20age%20for%20children%20to%20move%20out.%20In%20my%20experience%2C%20the%20real%20challenge%20is%20how%20families%20can%20age%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETransitioning%20from%20a%20parent-child%20relationship%20to%20an%20adult-adult%20one%20rewards%20both%20sides.%20Since%20moving%20home%2C%20I've%20gotten%20to%20know%20my%20parents%20more%20deeply.%20I've%20learned%20stories%20of%20their%20past%20and%20worries%20for%20their%20future%20that%20I%20never%20heard%20as%20a%20child%20and%20probably%20wouldn't%20have%20caught%20during%20occasional%20phone%20calls%20or%20holiday%20visits.%20Though%20the%20worst%20circumstances%20brought%20me%20back%20to%20my%20parents%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchange-relationship-with-parents-felt-like-adult-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebuilding%20our%20adult%20relationship%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20a%20silver%20lining.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20though%20headlines%20feature%20parents%20complaining%20their%20retirement%20plans%20are%20ruined%20by%20adult%20children%20moving%20home%2C%20I%20see%