20but%20fell%20ill%20in%20February.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I'm%20an%20aunt%20to%2012%20kids.%20Staying%20close%20to%20them%20as%20teenagers%20takes%20more%20effort%20than%20I%20expected.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222604%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20wearing%20a%20beanie%20and%20standing%20in%20the%20snow.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fa2d22405e0cf89dc87413%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221953%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20has%2012%20nieces%20and%20nephews.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Camilla%20Richardson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20have%20five%20siblings%2C%20and%20I'm%20the%20aunt%20to%2012%20nieces%20and%20nephews.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20felt%20easier%20to%20be%20close%20to%20them%20when%20they%20were%20younger.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAs%20some%20of%20them%20have%20gotten%20older%2C%20I've%20had%20to%20be%20more%20intentional%20about%20our%20relationships.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foldest-kid-foster-siblings-big-family-pros-cons-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efive%20siblings%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I'm%20the%20only%20one%20without%20children%2C%20meaning%20I%20got%20to%20be%20the%20%26quot%3Bfun%20aunt%26quot%3B%20who%20brought%20sweets%2C%20toys%2C%20games%2C%20and%20a%20heap%20of%20adoration%20for%20my%2012%20nieces%20and%20nephews.%20There's%20a%20favorite%20photo%20from%20the%20early%20years%20where%20two%20of%20my%20nephews%20stare%20at%20me%20in%20delight%2C%20one%20a%20newborn%20in%20my%20arms%20and%20the%20other%20not%20yet%202.%20That%20picture%20takes%20me%20back%20to%20when%20all%20I%20had%20to%20do%20was%20pretend%20to%20be%20a%20dinosaur%20or%20read%20them%20a%20picture%20book%2C%20and%20they%20thought%20I%20was%20the%20coolest%20person%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20they%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparents-say-teens-tough-love-raising-high-school-kids-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebecame%20teenagers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20things%20changed%20drastically%20overnight.%20I%20could%20tell%20from%20their%20lackluster%20responses%20to%20my%20offers%20to%20spend%20time%20together%20that%20they%20weren't%20interested.%20Most%20of%20them%20also%20dove%20into%20school%20sports%2C%20which%20had%20never%20been%20my%20strength%20or%20interest.%20I%20closed%20my%20eyes%20during%20every%20tackle%20at%20football%20games%2C%20terrified%20someone%20would%20get%20hurt%2C%20and%20finally%20decided%20to%20avoid%20in-person%20football%20altogether.%20It%20felt%20like%20we%20had%20nothing%20in%20common%20anymore%2C%20and%20I%20didn't%20know%20how%20to%20bridge%20the%20distance%20as%20friends%2C%20athletics%2C%20and%20independence%20became%20their%20focus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dcf06494-7460-429e-890d-31b6f3d06ba5%5C%22%3EI%20didn't%20know%20why%20we%20felt%20less%20close%20over%20the%20years%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20nieces%20and%20nephews%20range%20in%20age%20from%207%20to%2031.%20My%20two%20oldest%20nieces%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-to-new-different-state-relocating-reality-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eout%20of%20state%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20my%20relationship%20with%20them%20never%20fluctuated%20as%20they%20grew.%20Now%20in%20their%2020s%2C%20they%20still%20reach%20out%20to%20me%20to%20talk%2C%20and%20the%20eldest%20even%20asked%20me%20to%20be%20in%20her%20wedding%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20the%20highlights%20of%20my%20life.%20But%20with%20many%20of%20them%20who%20live%20closer%2C%20as%20they've%20gotten%20older%2C%20I%20wondered%20why%20things%20weren't%20so%20easy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20sought%20advice%20from%20people%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fplay-board-video-games-more-older-kids-than-toddlers-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eolder%20children%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20also%20called%20my%20sister%20and%20a%20sister-in-law.%20They%20all%20said%20the%20same%20thing%3A%20%26quot%3BYou%20just%20need%20to%20show%20up%20and%20be%20present.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20planned%20hangouts%20didn't%20work%2C%20I%20asked%20if%20I%20could%20come%20to%20the%20kids'%20basketball%20games.%20I%20asked%20about%20their%20current%20favorite%20music%20%E2%80%94%20names%20of%20artists%20I%20had%20usually%20never%20heard%20of%20%E2%80%94%20and%20then%20texted%20them%20about%20the%20songs%20after%20listening.%20I%20offered%20editing%20help%20with%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsuccessful-ivy-league-college-application-look-insider-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecollege%20essays%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20applications%2C%20which%20was%20a%20surprising%20win%20with%20an%20older%20nephew.%20And%20I%20began%20to%20notice%20a%20slight%20deepening%20and%20ease%20in%20our%20relationship%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222316%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20wearing%20a%20hat%20that%20says%20'Aunt'%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fa2d80405e0cf89dc87416%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221737%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20has%20learned%20that%20intentionality%20in%20her%20relationships%20helps%20her%20feel%20closer%20to%20her%20nieces%20and%20nephews.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Camilla%20Richardson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20change%20made%20me%20realize%20why%20things%20with%20my%20nieces%20out%20of%20state%20had%20remained%20steady.%20The%20distance%20required%20effort%20from%20the%20start%2C%20and%20that%20intentionality%20was%20built%20into%20our%20dynamic.%20I%20wrongly%20assumed%20closeness%20would%20simply%20carry%20over%20at%20any%20age%20with%20the%20kids%20closer%20in%20location.%20Being%20truly%20intentional%20was%20something%20I%20was%20learning%20to%20apply.%20An%20effort%20that's%20trial-and-error.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2221a2d8e6-8a07-4c3b-8de0-6551a700a107%5C%22%3EMy%20own%20aunts%20offer%20me%20a%20great%20example%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%20at%20my%20own%20aunts%2C%20I%20felt%20seen%20and%20genuinely%20liked%20by%20them.%20Even%20if%20we%20didn't%20see%20each%20other%20often%2C%20the%20warm%20way%20they%20looked%20at%20me%2C%20touched%20my%20arm%2C%20and%20asked%20questions%20when%20we%20saw%20each%20other%2C%20made%20me%20feel%20valued%20and%20cared%20for.%20It%20still%20does%20in%20my%2030s.%20I%20want%20to%20give%20that%20to%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcool-aunt-nieces-nephews-help-me-feel-less-alone-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enieces%20and%20nephews%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20too.%20Even%20if%20they%20don't%20have%20much%20to%20say%2C%20I%20hope%20they%20feel%20loved%20by%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20truth%20is%20that%20it's%20never%20going%20to%20be%20the%20same%20as%20when%20they%20were%20little.%20I'm%20learning%20to%20accept%20that%20the%20days%20of%20face%20painting%2C%20carrying%20them%20on%20my%20hip%2C%20and%20playing%20with%20dolls%20are%20over.%20I%20didn't%20realize%20that%20I%20would%20mourn%20that%20loss%20so%20much%20as%20an%20aunt.%20I%20still%20miss%20the%20times%20when%20all%20I%20had%20to%20do%20was%20sing%20a%20%3Cem%3EMoana%3C%2Fem%3E%20song%20to%20make%20them%20smile%2C%20but%20this%20new%20season%20has%20been%20rewarding%20in%20its%20own%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAunting%26quot%3B%20older%20kids%20has%20taken%20more%20effort%20and%20taught%20me%20a%20lot%20about%20connection%20and%20consistency.%20At%20the%20forefront%20of%20my%20mind%20is%20how%20lucky%20I%20am%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finternational-travel-niece-nephew-fun-aunt-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebe%20an%20aunt%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20these%20amazing%20humans%20at%20all%2C%20let%20alone%20twelve%20times%20over.%20They%20are%20truly%20the%20bright%20spots%20of%20my%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20I%20hope%20they%20see%20they%20have%20a%20lifelong%20cheerleader%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20grown%20they%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faunt-nieces-nephews-relationship-older-takes-effort-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778328661000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fa2d22405e0cf89dc87413%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faunt-nieces-nephews-relationship-older-takes-effort-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20have%2012%20nieces%20and%20nephews%20and%20love%20being%20the%20'cool%20aunt.'%20As%20they%20get%20older%2C%20though%2C%20staying%20close%20to%20them%20takes%20more%20effort.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Camilla%20Richardson)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Inside%20the%20Unprecedented%20Growth%20of%20Hasbro%E2%80%99s%20Magic%3A%20The%20Gathering%20and%20Trading%20Card%20Game%E2%80%99s%20High-Stakes%20Pro%20Competition%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778328000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236741966%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22For%20this%20week%E2%80%99s%20episode%20of%20%E2%80%9CStrictly%20Business%2C%E2%80%9D%20Variety%20was%20on%20the%20ground%20at%20MagicCon%202026%20in%20Las%20Vegas%2C%20a%20convention%20centered%20not%20around%20slight%20of%20hand%20tricks%2C%20but%20Hasbro%E2%80%99s%20hit%20trading%20card%20game%20Magic%3A%20The%20Gathering.%20The%20three-day%20event%20featured%2025%2C000%20attendees%20engaging%20in%20multiple%20activities%2C%20everything%20from%20a%20headliner%20panel%20featuring%20the%20MCU%E2%80%99s%20Paul%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D