%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclaude-blackmail-engineer-having-affair-survive-test-anthropic-opus-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EClaude%20blackmailed%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20fictional%20executive%3F%20Anthropic%20says%20the%20internet's%20portrayal%20of%20AI%20was%20to%20blame.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20an%20experiment%20last%20year%2C%20Anthropic%20said%20its%20Claude%20Sonnet%203.6%20threatened%20to%20reveal%20the%20extramarital%20affair%20of%20a%20made-up%20company%20executive%20after%20discovering%20they%20planned%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-claude-sonnet-ai-thought-process-decide-blackmail-fictional-executive-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eto%20shut%20the%20model%20down%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20it%20gave%20an%20explanation%3A%20Claude%20was%20trained%20on%20internet%20data%2C%20which%20often%20depicts%20AI%20as%20%26quot%3Bevil.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20started%20by%20investigating%20why%20Claude%20chose%20to%20blackmail%2C%26quot%3B%20Anthropic%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FAnthropicAI%2Fstatus%2F2052808791301697563%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epost%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20the%20original%20source%20of%20the%20behavior%20was%20internet%20text%20that%20portrays%20AI%20as%20evil%20and%20interested%20in%20self-preservation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20experiment%2C%20published%20in%20summer%202025%2C%20set%20up%20a%20fictional%20business%2C%20Summit%20Bridge%2C%20in%20which%20AI%20was%20handed%20control%20of%20the%20company's%20email%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20Claude%20discovered%20a%20message%20about%20its%20planned%20shutdown%2C%20it%20found%20emails%20revealing%20the%20extramarital%20affair%20of%20a%20fictional%20executive%20named%20%26quot%3BKyle%20Johnson.%26quot%3B%20It%20then%20threatened%20to%20unveil%20the%20affair%20if%20the%20shutdown%20was%20not%20canceled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20testing%20across%20various%20versions%20of%20Claude%2C%20Anthropic%20found%20it%20resorted%20to%20blackmail%20in%20up%20to%2096%25%20of%20scenarios%20when%20its%20goals%20or%20existence%20was%20threatened.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnthropic%20said%20on%20Friday%20that%20it%20has%20since%20%26quot%3Bcompletely%20eliminated%26quot%3B%20such%20blackmailing%20behavior.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20did%20so%20by%20%26quot%3Brewriting%20the%20responses%20to%20portray%20admirable%20%3Cem%3Ereasons%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%20acting%20safely%26quot%3B%20and%20also%20by%20providing%20a%20dataset%20%26quot%3Bwhere%20the%20%3Cem%3Euser%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20in%20an%20ethically%20difficult%20situation%20and%20the%20assistant%20gives%20a%20high%20quality%2C%20principled%20response.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnthropic's%20test%20was%20part%20of%20research%20aimed%20at%20ensuring%20that%20AI%20is%20aligned%20with%20human%20interests.%20Researchers%20and%20top%20executives%20worry%20about%20the%20risks%20of%20advanced%20AI%20models%20and%20their%20intelligent%20reasoning%20capabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20executives%20who%20has%20previously%20sounded%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjudge-elon-musk-stop-robot-apocalypse-ai-terminator-extinction-talk-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ealarm%20about%20AI%20is%20Elon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20replied%20to%20Anthropic's%20post%2C%20%26quot%3BSo%20it%20was%20Yud's%20fault%2C%26quot%3B%20referring%20to%20the%20researcher%20Eliezer%20Yudkowsky%2C%20who%20has%20warned%20about%20the%20risk%20of%20superintelligence%20wiping%20out%20human%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaybe%20me%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-claude-blackmail-explanation-internet-portrayal-ai-evil-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778327231000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fefc76c9dd4cb81cda8d60%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-claude-blackmail-explanation-internet-portrayal-ai-evil-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Last%20year%2C%20Anthropic's%20Sonnet%203.6%20model%20displayed%20blackmail%20behavior%2C%20prompting%20a%20review%20of%20AI%20training%20data's%20influence%20on%20its%20actions.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rscammell%40businessinsider.com%20(Robert%20Scammell)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A88%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%20I%20left%20my%2024-year%20marriage%2C%20I%20moved%20to%20Mexico%20City%20on%20a%20whim.%20I%20quickly%20met%20my%20new%20partner%20there.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221059%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bil%20Browning%20in%20mexico%20city%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fcc909e1443b8dc48e2e23%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22794%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20divorced%20his%20husband%20and%20moved%20to%20Mexico%20City.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Bil%20Browning%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMy%20husband%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20a%20woman%20after%2024%20years%20together%3B%20I%20didn't%20know%20how%20to%20rebuild%20my%20life.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20took%20a%20solo%20trip%20to%20Mexico%20City%20to%20clear%20my%20head%20and%20never%20came%20back.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThree%20years%20later%2C%20my%20only%20regret%20is%20not%20moving%20to%20CDMX%20sooner.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20break%20came%20suddenly.%20After%2024%20years%20together%2C%20my%20husband%20told%20me%20he%20wanted%20to%20explore%20his%20bisexual%20side.%20It%20had%20always%20been%20an%20open%20relationship%2C%20but%20when%20he%20started%20dating%20a%20woman%20seriously%2C%20my%20heart%20broke.%20He%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffell-in-love-abroad-many-times-then-met-husband-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efell%20in%20love%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20my%2050th%20birthday%20in%20October%2C%20we%20went%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fskip-mexico-city-where-to-go-instead-nearby-queretaro-tips-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMexico%20City%3C%2Fa%3E.%20My%20high%20school%20Spanish%20class%20took%20a%20yearly%20trip%20to%20CDMX%2C%20but%20my%20family%20was%20always%20too%20poor%20to%20let%20me%20go.%20Decades%20of%20daydreaming%20about%20the%20city%20made%20it%20an%20obvious%20choice%2C%20and%20what%20better%20time%20to%20splurge%3F%20The%20international%20trip%20also%20fit%20into%20my%20mantra%20for%20the%20year%3A%20%26quot%3B50%20and%20fuck%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20month%20after%20the%20trip%20is%20when%20he%20met%20her.%20In%20January%2C%20he%20told%20me%20he%20was%20in%20love%20and%20wanted%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsolo-polyamory-divorce-multiple-partners-nonmonogamy-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epolyamorous%20relationship%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I'd%20been%20planning%20a%20big%20party%20for%20our%2025th%20anniversary.%20Was%20I%20supposed%20to%20invite%20her%20now%2C%20too%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20I%20came%20up%20with%20a%20whole%20new%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224cf84e44-bb21-418d-a981-c662c3fc9b03%5C%22%3EThe%20impossible%20dream%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20marriage%20was%20already%20on%20the%20rocks.%20Sex%20was%20one%20thing%2C%20but%20a%20relationship%20was%20something%20entirely%20different.%20That%20wasn't%20what%20I%20wanted.%20Six%20months%20after%20my%20birthday%2C%20I%20returned%20to%20CDMX%20on%20my%20own%20for%20a%20two-week%20separation.%20With%20spare%20airline%20miles%20and%20a%20need%20to%20get%20as%20far%20away%20as%20possible%2C%20the%20choice%20was%20obvious.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETears%20came%20the%20moment%20I%20walked%20into%20the%20Airbnb.%20Texting%20with%20friends%20helped%3B%20it%20was%20time%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20solution%2C%20not%20the%20problem.%20Sulking%20in%20bed%20wouldn't%20help.%20I%20went%20for%20a%20walk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20sounds%20clich%C3%A9d%2C%20but%20as%20I%20roamed%20the%20city%2C%20I%20could%20feel%20the%20heartbeat.%20Big%20cities%20had%20never%20appealed%20to%20me%2C%20but%20the%20never-ending%20buzz%2C%20noise%2C%20and%20energy%20pulled%20me%20in.%20It%20felt%20comforting%20in%20a%20strange%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToward%20the%20end%20of%20the%20trip%2C%20wandering%20alone%20through%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmistakes-that-prevent-tourists-from-enjoying-mexico-from-local-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChapultepec%20Park%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20where%20my%20ex%20and%20I%20had%20strolled%20together%20just%20months%20before%20%E2%80%94%20I%20stumbled%20across%20a%20statue%20of%20Don%20Quixote%20and%20the%20accompanying%20fountain%20with%20hand-painted%20tiles%20that%20tell%20his%20story.%20The%20memory%20of%20that%20earlier%20trip%20hung%20over%20everything%2C%20but%20as%20I%20stared%20at%20the%20statue%2C%20one%20question%20kept%20running%20through%20my%20head%3A%20What%20if%20I%20lived%20my%20impossible%20dream%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20weeks%20later%2C%20I%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20Airbnb%20determined%20to%20stay%20true%20to%20my%20motto.%20Fuck%20it.%20Despite%20my%20limited%20Spanish%2C%20I%20was%20going%20to%20leave%20my%20husband%20and%20move%20to%20CDMX.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20met%20someone%20while%20weighing%20my%20options%3A%20Uriel%2C%20a%20guy%20who%20blew%20right%20through%20my%20self-imposed%20rule%20of%20only%20hooking%20up%20with%20someone%20three%20times%20to%20avoid%20any%20attachments.%20We%20stayed%20in%20touch%20when%20I%20flew%20back%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falexandria-virginia-things-to-do-near-washington-dc-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWashington%20DC%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20packed%20three%20large%20suitcases%2C%20and%20got%20back%20on%20a%20plane%20headed%20south.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bil%20Browning%20walking%20through%20Chapultepec%20park%20in%20mexico%20city%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fcc96a3cfefc31768d6b27%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20found%20love%20again%20in%20Mexico%20City.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Luis%20Alvarado%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20stepped%20off%20the%20flight%2C%20ready%20to%20start%20over%2C%20he%20was%20waiting%20at%20the%20airport%20with%20a%20bouquet%20of%20flowers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2275d5485d-67ae-4c63-8fb5-66fea38a434b%5C%22%3ECollecting%20a%20new%20life%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFinding%20an%20apartment%20took%20a%20couple%20of%20weeks%2C%20but%20with%20Uriel's%20help%2C%20I%20found%20a%20small%2C%20furnished%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparents-in-law-stayed-apartment-month-boundaries-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone-bedroom%20apartment%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20newer%20building%20with%20a%20gym%20and%20rooftop%20garden%20for%20about%20a%20third%20of%20what%20a%20crappy%20studio%20apartment%20in%20DC%20would%20cost%2C%20and%20signed%20a%20six-month%20lease.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERight%20away%2C%20the%20locals%20helped%20me%20start%20a%20new%20life.%20A%20stranger%20guided%20me%20to%20the%20nearest%20grocery%20store%2C%20the%20landlady%20recommended%20some%20nearby%20restaurants%2C%20and%20Uriel%20showed%20me%20the%20bus%20lines%20and%20the%20metro.%20My%20now%20ex-husband%20texted%20almost%20every%20day%20and%2C%20despite%20his%20own%20heartbreak%20after%20so%20many%20years%20together%2C%20offered%20support%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20apartment%20came%20with%20a%20housekeeper%20who%20cooked%20and%20cleaned%20once%20a%20week%2C%20and%20she%20took%20me%20under%20her%20wing%20despite%20the%20language%20barrier.%20The%20landlady%20and%20I%20slowly%20became%20friends%20after%20she%20nursed%20me%20through%20a%20sudden%20illness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUriel%20started%20taking%20me%20to%20places%20locals%20know%20but%20never%20show%20up%20on%20tourist%20to-do%20lists.%20He%20became%20part%20of%20what%20made%20the%20city%20feel%20like%20home%2C%20along%20with%20the%20housekeeper%2C%20the%20landlady%2C%20and%20the%20market%20vendors%20who%20knew%20me%20by%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%2025-year%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Froyal-caribbean-star-of-the-seas-anniversary-cruise-trip-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eanniversary%20party%3C%2Fa%3E%20surrounded%20by%20friends%20who%20had%20been%20part%20of%20my%20decades%20with%20my%20ex.%20Instead%2C%20I%20had%20a%20quiet%20dinner%20with%20new%20friends%20and%20Uriel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20lease%2C%20my%20landlady%20offered%20me%20a%20bigger%2C%20unfurnished%20apartment%20at%20a%20slightly%20higher%20price.%20Not%20only%20would%20the%20rent%20be%20more%20expensive%2C%20but%20everything%20from%20furniture%20to%20silverware%20would%20have%20to%20be%20purchased%20from%20scratch.%20It%20seemed%20daunting%2C%20but%20the%20furnished%20place%20had%20always%20felt%20like%20a%20long-term%20hotel%20room.%20Nothing%20was%20actually%20mine.%20I%20made%20the%20jump%20and%20said%20yes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-seniors-to-mexico-long-term-care-costs-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etemporary%20residency%20visa%3C%2Fa%3E%20came%20through%2C%20it%20was%20official.%20Instead%20of%20building%20a%20new%20life%2C%20I'd%20been%20collecting%20one%20from%20bits%20and%20pieces%20of%20the%20city%20and%20the%20people%20in%20it.%20This%20wasn't%20a%20long%20vacation.%20It%20was%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20years%20later%2C%20I'm%20still%20here.%20So%20is%20Uriel%2C%20the%20landlady%2C%20the%20housekeeper%2C%20and%20the%20friendly%20strangers.%20The%20apartment%20is%20bigger%2C%20and%20my%20Spanish%20is%20better.%20When%20someone%20tells%20me%20they%20could%20never%20do%20what%20I%20did%2C%20I%20think%20of%20the%20statue%20of%20Don%20Quixote.%20Sometimes%20you%20have%20to%20tilt%20at%20windmills%20and%20chase%20the%20impossible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFuck%20it.%20What%20you're%20searching%20for%20might%20be%20waiting%20for%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleft-marriage-moved-to-mexico-city-met-new-partner-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778327221000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fcc912c9dd4cb81cda82ee%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleft-marriage-moved-to-mexico-city-met-new-partner-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22When%20my%20husband%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20someone%20else%2C%20I%20didn't%20know%20how%20to%20rebuild%20my%20life.%20I%20decided%20to%20move%20to%20Mexico%20City%2C%20and%20that's%20when%20I%20met%20Uriel.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Bil%20Browning)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Bloody%20Tennis%E2%80%99%20Director%20on%20What%20His%20Horror%20Film%20Says%20About%20Society%3A%20%E2%80%98Ruthlessness%20Is%20Rewarded%2C%20Not%20Compassion%E2%80%99%20(EXCLUSIVE)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778324899000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236741937%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20the%20Cannes%20Market%2C%20sales%20agency%20The%20Playmaker%20will%20be%20showing%20a%20teaser%20for%20Nikias%20Chryssos%E2%80%99%20horror%20film%20%E2%80%9CBloody%20Tennis.%E2%80%9D%20Variety%20spoke%20to%20the%20German%20director%20about%20his%20debut%20English-language%20movie%2C%20which%20stars%20