Research%20and%20Development%20in%20India%3A%20A%20State%20Perspective%20published%20by%20the%20ICAR-%20Directorate%20of%20Cashew%20Research%2C%20Karnataka%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20coastal%20state%20of%20Kerala%20accounts%20for%2015%20percent%20of%20cashew%20production%20in%20India.%20Of%20this%2C%20Kannur%20district%20accounts%20for%20nearly%2063%20percent%20of%20the%20total%20cashew%20cultivation%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECashew%20production%20is%20relatively%20high%20in%20Kannur%20because%20the%20region%20experiences%20a%20prolonged%20dry%20spell%20during%20the%20reproductive%20phase%20of%20the%20crop.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrijith%2C%20who%20hails%20from%20the%20same%20district%20and%20grows%20cashew%20on%2013%20acres%20of%20land%2C%20shares%20that%20cashew%20productivity%20has%20been%20affected%20amid%20unseasonal%20rain%20and%20extreme%20weather%20conditions%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20experience%20unseasonal%20rains%20in%20March-May.%20This%20affects%20the%20pollination%20process%20and%20the%20harvesting%20period.%20We%20are%20small%20farmers%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20good%20storage%20facilities.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20we%20have%20to%20keep%20our%20harvest%20out%20in%20the%20open.%20Most%20of%20this%20produce%20gets%20wet%20in%20this%20period%20then.%20No%20cashew%20factory%20is%20ready%20to%20purchase%20this%20damaged%20product%20as%20its%20quality%20becomes%20poor%2C%20colour%20gets%20faded%2C%20and%20also%20has%20a%20poor%20taste%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20the%2047-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcashew-2-1725551452.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Brijith%20makes%20sprouted%20cashew%20nuts%20and%20supplies%20to%20major%20food%20supply%20companies%20and%20hotels%20in%20Kerala.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcashew-2-1725551452.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcashew-2-1725551452-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcashew-2-1725551452-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcashew-2-1725551452-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcashew-2-1725551452-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-364788%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBrijith%20makes%20sprouted%20cashew%20nuts%20and%20supplies%20to%20major%20food%20supply%20companies%20and%20hotels%20in%20Kerala.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20conventional%20practice%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F181811%2Fias-hero-odisha-district-cashew-empowerment-farmers-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecashew%20farming%20%3C%2Fa%3Einvolves%20harvesting%20the%20nuts%20for%20consumption%20as%20dry%20fruits%20or%20in%20a%20roasted%20form%2C%20there%20was%20a%20limited%20scope%20for%20value%20addition.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20can%20dry%20and%20store%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F354850%2Fhomemaker-entrepreneur-organic-coconut-greenaura-oil-pickles-business-kerala-sumila-jayaraj%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecoconut%20produce%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20can%20make%20mango%20pulp%20but%20there%20is%20hardly%20any%20alternative%20to%20utilise%20cashews%20in%20other%20forms%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecognising%20this%20as%20a%20crucial%20gap%20in%20the%20market%2C%20Brijith%20embarked%20on%20a%20journey%20of%20experimentation.%20He%20reached%20out%20to%20institutions%20like%20Central%20Food%20Technological%20Research%20Institute%20(CFTRI)%20Mysuru%2C%20and%20Kerala%20Agriculture%20University%20to%20explore%20the%20nutritional%20benefits%20and%20viability%20of%20sprouting%20cashews.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20receiving%20an%20encouraging%20response%20from%20the%20institutes%2C%20his%20focus%20shifted%20towards%20refining%20the%20sprouting%20technology%20for%20cashews.%20Recognising%20the%20perishable%20nature%20of%20cashews%20and%20the%20challenges%20in%20maintaining%20a%20cold%20supply%20chain%2C%20he%20drew%20inspiration%20from%20Japan%E2%80%99s%20retorting%20technology%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%20which%20involves%20heat-treating%20food%20in%20airtight%20containers%20to%20extend%20shelf%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20adapting%20this%20innovative%20approach%2C%20he%20devised%20a%20method%20to%20process%20and%20store%20sprouted%20cashews%20at%20room%20temperature%2C%20enhancing%20their%20shelf%20life%20and%20market%20reach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20year%20into%20research%20and%20development%2C%20Brijith%20started%20his%20own%20startup%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20raw%20sprouts%2C%20pickles%20to%20manchurian%2C%20soup%20premix%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20initial%20challenges%20that%20Brijith%20tackled%20was%20the%20limited%20germination%20potential%20of%20cashews.%20%E2%80%9CDue%20to%20their%20seasonal%20nature%2C%20the%20germination%20potential%20of%20matured%20cashews%20was%20only%2090%20days.%20Therefore%2C%20year%20round%20availability%20was%20a%20big%20concern.%20Through%20persistent%20research%2C%20trials%2C%20and%20development%20efforts%2C%20I%20successfully%20extended%20the%20germination%20potential%20to%20180-200%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20an%20initial%20investment%20of%20Rs%201%20lakh%2C%20Brijith%20secured%20a%20grant%20of%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20from%20the%20central%20government%20under%20the%20Rashtriya%20Krishi%20Vikas%20Yojana%20(RKVY)%20sc